test_cases.objective: Verify user can sign in with valid email and password
test_steps: Navigate to login page
Click on 'Continue' button using email input
Enter valid email and password
Click on 'Continue' button after entering password
Verify user is authenticated successfully
expected_results: Login page displays correctly with sign in options
Email field is displayed with correct label and placeholder
Password field is displayed with correct label and required attribute
Continue button is clickable and takes user to password step
User can enter valid email and password
User can click on continue button after entering password
User is authenticated successfully
